{"tid":129090,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【接放工】你地覺得條女啱定我啱？","createTime":"2017-02-21T10:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T05:53:39.000Z","uid":45713,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce035b52b6a820d0c14da2e57397c40d3855878","tid":129090,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"我由追佢戈陣，<br />\n佢成日叫我接佢放工食宵夜<br />\n到一齊咗一個月我都有接佢<br />\n咁尋晚，佢同我呻佢好多嘢做，<br />\n咁我聽完佢呻傾完，知佢多嘢忙<br />\n後來咪問佢：咁不如我唔來啦？你快啲番去做嘢<br />\n佢答：好<br />\n<br />\n之後我見佢自己一個搭車<br />\n諗住打俾佢陪佢傾電話傾到番屋企<br />\n我問佢係邊<br />\n佢話同同事食緊嘢<br />\n<br />\n我真係燥到仆街<br />\n你一開始同我講約同事食嘢我咪唔嚟<br />\n扮乜嘢忙"},{"pid":"e956deceeed5b55dd6e507d9927872790317f0ef","tid":129090,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"約同事食野有咩問題？<br />\n你一樣可以等佢食完 送佢返去"},{"pid":"6d75999a0069562cd5558f2acad6c589e3d67b07","tid":129090,"uid":11759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"你有得抖一晚仲想點"},{"pid":"6191f343d6e030db5893155f1eed0f1938d59d09","tid":129090,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約同事食野有咩問題？<br />\n你一樣可以等佢食完 送佢返去</blockquote><br />\n冇問題<br />\n一早講想同同事食咪得"},{"pid":"5cebd94b72af58933a931dbe2e358228b0873e6d","tid":129090,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有得抖一晚仲想點</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a550c3d61ece64c5924a8c43c03cdd432db04dca","tid":129090,"uid":72094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有得抖一晚仲想點</blockquote><br />\n巴打好大怨氣"},{"pid":"9c7edfdd42e2f254f0266e08afd77af289425de0","tid":129090,"uid":23810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係嬲條女講大話?"},{"pid":"8c807806930e7d59eca7e9fe36302add52e465da","tid":129090,"uid